[package]
name = "alacritty_config"
version = "0.1.2-dev"
authors = [ "Christian Duerr <contact@christianduerr.com>",]
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
description = "Alacritty configuration abstractions"
homepage = "https://github.com/alacritty/alacritty"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.70.0"

[dependencies]
serde = "1.0.163"
toml = "0.8.2"

[dependencies.log]
version = "0.4.17"
features = [ "serde",]

[package]
name = "alacritty_config_derive"
version = "0.2.2-dev"
authors = [ "Christian Duerr <contact@christianduerr.com>",]
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
description = "Failure resistant deserialization derive"
homepage = "https://github.com/alacritty/alacritty"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.70.0"

[lib]
proc-macro = true

[dependencies]
proc-macro2 = "1.0.24"
quote = "1.0.7"

[dev-dependencies]
log = "0.4.11"
toml = "0.8.2"

[dependencies.syn]
version = "2.0.16"
features = [ "derive", "parsing", "proc-macro", "printing",]
default-features = false

[dev-dependencies.alacritty_config]
path = "../alacritty_config"
version = "0.1.2-dev"

[dev-dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.117"
features = [ "derive",]

[package]
name = "alacritty_terminal"
version = "0.20.0-dev"
authors = [ "Christian Duerr <contact@christianduerr.com>", "Joe Wilm <joe@jwilm.com>",]
license = "Apache-2.0"
description = "Library for writing terminal emulators"
readme = "../README.md"
homepage = "https://github.com/alacritty/alacritty"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.70.0"

[dependencies]
base64 = "0.21.3"
home = "0.5.5"
libc = "0.2"
log = "0.4"
parking_lot = "0.12.0"
polling = "3.0.0"
regex-automata = "0.3.6"
serde_yaml = "0.9.25"
toml = "0.8.2"
unicode-width = "0.1"

[dev-dependencies]
serde_json = "1.0.0"

[dependencies.alacritty_config_derive]
path = "../alacritty_config_derive"
version = "0.2.2-dev"

[dependencies.alacritty_config]
path = "../alacritty_config"
version = "0.1.2-dev"

[dependencies.bitflags]
version = "2.2.1"
features = [ "serde",]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
features = [ "derive", "rc",]

[dependencies.vte]
version = "0.12.0"
default-features = false
features = [ "ansi", "serde",]

[target."cfg(unix)".dependencies]
rustix-openpty = "0.1.1"
signal-hook = "0.3.10"

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies]
piper = "0.2.1"
miow = "0.6.0"

[target."cfg(windows)".dependencies.windows-sys]
version = "0.48.0"
features = [ "Win32_System_Console", "Win32_Foundation", "Win32_Security", "Win32_System_LibraryLoader", "Win32_System_Threading", "Win32_System_WindowsProgramming",]

[package]
name = "cosmic-text"
description = "Pure Rust multi-line text handling"
version = "0.7.0"
authors = [ "Jeremy Soller <jeremy@system76.com>",]
edition = "2021"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/cosmic-text/latest/cosmic_text/"

[dependencies]
libm = "0.2.6"
log = "0.4.17"
unicode-linebreak = "0.1.4"
unicode-script = "0.5.5"
unicode-segmentation = "1.10.0"
rangemap = "1.2.0"
parking_lot = "0.12.1"
once_cell = "1.17.1"
ttf-parser = "0.18.1"
stretto = "0.8.1"

[features]
default = [ "std", "swash",]
no_std = [ "rustybuzz/libm",]
std = [ "fontdb/memmap", "fontdb/std", "fontdb/fontconfig", "ouroboros/std", "rustybuzz/std", "sys-locale", "unicode-bidi/std",]
vi = [ "syntect",]

[workspace]
members = [ "examples/*",]

[dependencies.fontdb]
version = "0.16.0"
default-features = false

[dependencies.ouroboros]
version = "0.15.5"
default-features = false

[dependencies.rustybuzz]
version = "0.8.0"

features = [ "libm",]

[dependencies.swash]
version = "0.1.8"
optional = true

[dependencies.syntect]
version = "5.0.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.sys-locale]
version = "0.2.3"
optional = true

[dependencies.peniko]
git = "https://github.com/linebender/peniko"
rev = "cafdac9a211a0fb2fec5656bd663d1ac770bcc81"

[dependencies.unicode-bidi]
version = "0.3.8"
default-features = false
features = [ "hardcoded-data",]

[package]

[package.license]

[dependencies.rfd]

[dependencies.peniko]

[dependencies.parking_lot]

[dependencies.floem_renderer]

[dependencies.floem_vger]

[dependencies.image]

[dependencies.copypasta]
version = "0.10.0"
default-features = false
features = [ "wayland", "x11",]

[workspace.package]

[package]

resvg = "0.33.0"

[dependencies.image]

[dependencies.cosmic-text]

[dependencies.peniko]
git = "https://github.com/linebender/peniko"

[dependencies.vger]
git = "https://github.com/lapce/vger-rs"
rev = "ed10537c72a732a03f782225a39da80e6f9acbbe"

[dependencies.image]
version = "0.24"
features = [ "jpeg", "png",]

[dependencies.floem_renderer]
path = "../renderer"

[package]

[package]
name = "tracing"
version = "0.2.0"
authors = [ "Eliza Weisman <eliza@buoyant.io>", "Tokio Contributors <team@tokio.rs>",]
license = "MIT"
readme = "README.md"
repository = "https://github.com/tokio-rs/tracing"
homepage = "https://tokio.rs"
description = "Application-level tracing for Rust.\n"
categories = [ "development-tools::debugging", "development-tools::profiling", "asynchronous", "no-std",]
keywords = [ "logging", "tracing", "metrics", "async",]
edition = "2018"
rust-version = "1.56.0"

[dependencies]
pin-project-lite = "0.2.9"

[dev-dependencies]
log = "0.4.17"

[features]
default = [ "std", "attributes",]
max_level_off = []
max_level_error = []
max_level_warn = []
max_level_info = []
max_level_debug = []
max_level_trace = []
release_max_level_off = []
release_max_level_error = []
release_max_level_warn = []
release_max_level_info = []
release_max_level_debug = []
release_max_level_trace = []
alloc = [ "tracing-core/alloc",]
std = [ "tracing-core/std", "alloc",]
log-always = [ "log",]
attributes = [ "tracing-attributes",]

[dependencies.tracing-core]
path = "../tracing-core"
version = "0.2"
default-features = false

[dependencies.log]
version = "0.4.17"
optional = true

[dependencies.tracing-attributes]
path = "../tracing-attributes"
version = "0.2"
optional = true

[dev-dependencies.criterion]
version = "0.3.6"
default_features = false

[dev-dependencies.futures]
version = "0.3.21"
default_features = false

[dev-dependencies.tracing-mock]
path = "../tracing-mock"

[badges.maintenance]
status = "actively-developed"

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dev-dependencies]
wasm-bindgen-test = "0.3.31"

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
all-features = true
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]

[[bench]]
name = "bench"
harness = false

[package]
name = "tracing-appender"
version = "0.2.0"
authors = [ "Zeki Sherif <zekshi@amazon.com>", "Tokio Contributors <team@tokio.rs>",]
license = "MIT"
readme = "README.md"
repository = "https://github.com/tokio-rs/tracing"
homepage = "https://tokio.rs"
description = "Provides utilities for file appenders and making non-blocking writers.\n"
categories = [ "development-tools::debugging", "asynchronous",]
keywords = [ "logging", "tracing", "file-appender", "non-blocking-writer",]
edition = "2018"
rust-version = "1.53.0"

[dependencies]
crossbeam-channel = "0.5.5"
thiserror = "1.0.31"

[dev-dependencies]
tempfile = "3.3.0"

[dependencies.time]
version = "0.3.2"
default-features = false
features = [ "formatting", "parsing",]

[dependencies.parking_lot]
optional = true
version = "0.12.1"

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
path = "../tracing-subscriber"
version = "0.3"
default-features = false
features = [ "fmt", "std",]

[dev-dependencies.criterion]
version = "0.3.6"
default_features = false

[dev-dependencies.tracing]
path = "../tracing"
version = "0.2"

[dev-dependencies.time]
version = "0.3.2"
default-features = false
features = [ "formatting", "parsing",]

[package]
name = "tracing-attributes"
version = "0.2.0"
authors = [ "Tokio Contributors <team@tokio.rs>", "Eliza Weisman <eliza@buoyant.io>", "David Barsky <dbarsky@amazon.com>",]
repository = "https://github.com/tokio-rs/tracing"
homepage = "https://tokio.rs"
description = "Procedural macro attributes for automatically instrumenting functions.\n"
categories = [ "development-tools::debugging", "development-tools::profiling", "asynchronous",]
keywords = [ "logging", "tracing", "macro", "instrument", "log",]
license = "MIT"
readme = "README.md"
edition = "2018"
rust-version = "1.56.0"

[lib]
proc-macro = true

[dependencies]
proc-macro2 = "1.0.40"
quote = "1.0.20"

[dev-dependencies]
tokio-test = "0.4.2"
async-trait = "0.1.67"
trybuild = "1.0.64"
rustversion = "1.0.9"

[dependencies.syn]
version = "2.0"
default-features = false
features = [ "full", "parsing", "printing", "visit-mut", "clone-impls", "extra-traits", "proc-macro",]

[dev-dependencies.tracing]
path = "../tracing"
version = "0.2"

[dev-dependencies.tracing-mock]
path = "../tracing-mock"
features = [ "tokio-test",]

[dev-dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
path = "../tracing-subscriber"
version = "0.3"
features = [ "env-filter",]

[badges.maintenance]
status = "experimental"

[package]
name = "tracing-core"
version = "0.2.0"
authors = [ "Tokio Contributors <team@tokio.rs>",]
license = "MIT"
readme = "README.md"
repository = "https://github.com/tokio-rs/tracing"

[features]

[package.metadata.docs.rs]

[package]
name = "tracing-log"

authors = [ "Tokio Contributors <team@tokio.rs>",]

repository = "https://github.com/tokio-rs/tracing"

[dependencies.tracing-core]

[package]

authors = [ "Eliza Weisman <eliza@buoyant.io>", "David Barsky <me@davidbarsky.com>", "Tokio Contributors <team@tokio.rs>",]

license = "MIT"
readme = "README.md"

[package]
